      How to Find Your Perfect Length
    </h2>
    <p class="care-intro reveal">Not sure which length is right? Here is the easiest way to measure:</p>

    <ol class="measure-steps reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <li>Grab a soft tape measure, a piece of string, or a thin strip of paper.</li>
      <li>Loop it loosely around your neck (or your daughter's neck) — not too tight, just comfortable.</li>
      <li>Hold it at the point where you'd like the pendant to sit.</li>
      <li>Measure the length from that point. That number is your ideal necklace length.</li>
      <li>Add 1&quot;–2&quot; if you prefer more breathing room or a looser drape.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="care-closing reveal">Questions? We are here for you — <a href="mailto:support@lilytily.com" style="color:var(--rose-gold);">support@lilytily.com</a></p>
